where $\psi(z)$ is the logarithmic derivative of Gamma function \cite{GR}.
The expression (\ref{Tot})  is exact in $a$ in the subcritical range and $\alpha$, is odd (even) with respect to $a$ ($\alpha$). It  is in agreement  with result obtained in \cite{12} for $\alpha=0$;
the coefficient of the $a^3$ term at $\alpha=0$ was also found in perturbation
